      "daily_routine_templates": "⏱ Violezo vya ratiba ya kila siku",
      "pre_built_sequences_of_activities_that": "Mfululizo uliotengenezwa mapema wa shughuli zinazolingana na vipindi vya kawaida vya muda (dakika 10, dakika 30, dakika 45). Chagua kimoja na ukifuate.",
