      "5_19_3_16_95_15_16_inches_8_feet": "5 × 19 3/16 = 95 15/16 inchi ≈ futi 8",
      "each_16_inches_has_a_black_diamond_for": "Kila inchi 16 ina almasi nyeusi kwa nafasi ya kawaida ya nguzo.",
      "measuring_cups": "Vikombe vya kupimia",
      "a_standard_set_includes_1_cup_1_2_1_3_": "Seti ya kawaida inajumuisha kikombe 1, 1/2, 1/3, 1/4. Baadhi ya seti huongeza 2/3 na 3/4. Vikombe vya glasi vya kupimia vina alama za 1/4, 1/3, 1/2, 2/3, 3/4 kikombe na kikombe 1.",
