      "multiply_top_and_bottom_by_the_same_nu": "Zidisha juu NA chini kwa namba ile ile; thamani hubaki. ½ = 2/4 = 50/100 = 0.5 = 50%. Sehemu sawa ni daraja kati ya sehemu, desimali, na asilimia.",
