      "extremely_dangerous_mixing_bleach_naoc": "Hatari sana! Kuchanganya bleach (NaOCl) na amonia hutengeneza gesi ya chloramine yenye sumu. Imesababisha vifo katika maabara na nyumbani. Kamwe usichanganye bleach na kemikali nyingine yoyote.",
