      "ammonia_or_acids": "Amonia au asidi",
      "bleach_ammonia_chloramine_gas_toxic_bl": "Bleach + amonia = gesi ya chloramine (sumu). Bleach + asidi = gesi ya chlorine (sumu). Zote zinaweza kusababisha jeraha kubwa la kupumua au kifo. Kamwe usichanganye bleach na kemikali.",
