      "600_000_sandhill_cranes_gather_here_ea": "Korongo 600,000 aina ya Sandhill hukusanyika hapa kila majira ya kuchipua — mojawapo ya maonyesho ya kuvutia zaidi ya asili",
      "great_salt_lake": "Great Salt Lake",
      "5_million_migratory_birds_depend_on_th": "Ndege wahamiaji milioni 5 hutegemea bahari hii ya bara kama kituo cha kuongeza mafuta",
      "mississippi_delta": "Delta ya Mississippi",
      "wetlands_here_support_40_of_north_amer": "Ardhioevu hapa husaidia 40% ya ndege wa maji wahamiaji wa Amerika Kaskazini",
      "chesapeake_bay": "Chesapeake Bay",
      "largest_estuary_in_the_us_critical_win": "Mlango mkubwa zaidi wa mto nchini Marekani — makazi muhimu ya majira ya baridi kwa bata na bata bukini",
      "atlantic": "Atlantiki",
      "mississippi": "Mississippi",
      "central": "Kati",
