      "flight_metabolic_rate_0_8_kcal_hr": "Kiwango cha kimetaboliki ya safari: ~0.8 kcal/saa",
      "crossing_time_20_hours_at_25_mph": "Muda wa kuvuka: ~saa 20 kwa 25 mph",
      "energy_required_16_kcal": "Nishati inayohitajika: ~16 kcal",
      "margin_of_safety_2_kcal_11": "Ukingo wa usalama: ~2 kcal (11%)",
      "that_is_an_incredibly_thin_margin_a_st": "Huo ni ukingo mwembamba mno. Upepo mkali wa mbele, mpaka wa baridi, au kufika pwani na upungufu wa uzito wa 10% kunaweza kuwa mauti. Ndiyo maana ubora wa makazi ya kituo cha kusimama ni ",
      "literally_life_or_death": "suala la uhai au kifo kihalisi",
      "for_migratory_birds": " kwa ndege wahamiaji.",
