      "bike_infrastructure": "Miundombinu ya Baiskeli",
      "dutch_cycling_cities_have_1_3_the_tran": "Miji ya baiskeli ya Uholanzi ina 1/3 ya hewa chafu ya usafiri. Miundombinu huunda tabia.",
      "building_retrofits": "Uboreshaji wa Majengo",
      "insulation_heat_pumps_led_lighting_us_": "Insuleti + pampu za joto + taa za LED. Majengo ya Marekani hutumia 40% ya nishati ya msingi.",
      "heat_pumps": "Pampu za Joto",
      "3_4_more_efficient_than_gas_furnaces_w": "Zenye ufanisi 3–4× zaidi ya matanuru ya gesi. Hufanya kazi hadi −15°C katika modeli za kisasa za hali ya hewa baridi.",
