      "venous_return": "Kurudi kwa Damu ya Mishipa",
      "deoxygenated_blood_returns_through_ven": "Damu isiyo na oksijeni hurudi kupitia venuli na mishipa, ikisaidiwa na pampu za misuli na vali, hadi atriamu ya kulia.",
      "path_of_air": "Njia ya Hewa",
      "trace_the_journey_of_a_breath_of_air_f": "Fuatilia safari ya pumzi ya hewa kutoka puani hadi alveoli na kurudi.",
      "nasal_cavity_2": "Tundu la Pua",
      "air_enters_through_the_nostrils_and_is": "Hewa huingia kupitia matundu ya pua na hupashwa joto, hutiwa unyevu, na huchujwa na utando wa ute na turbineti.",
      "pharynx_2": "Koromeo",
      "air_passes_through_the_nasopharynx_and": "Hewa hupita kupitia nasopharynx na oropharynx, njia inayoshirikiwa na njia ya chakula.",
      "larynx": "Zoloto",
      "air_crosses_the_vocal_cords_in_the_voi": "Hewa huvuka nyuzi za sauti katika sanduku la sauti. Epiglottis hulinda dhidi ya chakula kuingia njia ya hewa.",
      "trachea_2": "Umio wa Hewa",
      "the_trachea_windpipe_is_reinforced_by_": "Umio wa hewa huimarishwa na pete za gegedu zenye umbo la C. Silia husogeza ute juu ili kunasa uchafu.",
      "bronchi": "Bronchi",
      "the_trachea_splits_into_left_and_right": "Umio wa hewa hugawanyika kuwa bronchi kuu za kushoto na kulia, kila moja huingia pafu moja. Zinagawanyika kuwa bronchioli ndogo.",
      "alveoli_2": "Alveoli",
      "300_million_grape_like_sacs_where_gas_": "Vifuko milioni 300 vinavyofanana na zabibu ambapo ubadilishaji wa gesi hutokea. O2 husambaa ndani ya damu; CO2 husambaa nje. Eneo la uso ni sawa na uwanja wa tenisi.",
      "exhalation": "Kutoa Pumzi",
      "the_diaphragm_relaxes_and_rises_reduci": "Kiwambo hulegea na kupanda, kikipunguza ujazo wa pafu. Hewa yenye CO2 nyingi husukumwa nje kupitia njia ile ile kinyume.",
