      "dna_genetics_lab": "🧬 DNA / Maabara ya Jenetiki",
      "build_replicate_transcribe_translate_m": "Jenga • Nakili • Andika • Tafsiri • Badilisha • CRISPR • Uchunguzi wa Kimahakama",
      "build_the_double_helix_from_4_letters": "Jenga double helix kutoka herufi 4",
      "a_pairs_with_t_2_bonds_g_with_c_3_wats": "A hujiunga na T (bond 2), G na C (3). Watson + Crick + Franklin (1953) walitatua umbo hili kutoka X-ray crystallography. Umbo hilo linaonyesha jinsi DNA inavyojinakili yenyewe na kusomwa.",
      "replicate_unzip_copy_rezip": "Nakili — fungua, nakili, funga tena",
      "helicase_splits_the_strands_dna_polyme": "Helicase inagawanya strand; DNA polymerase inajenga strand ya ziada. Semi-conservative — kila helix mpya ina strand moja ya zamani + moja mpya. Meselson na Stahl walithibitisha hili mwaka 1958.",
      "transcribe_dna_mrna_in_the_nucleus": "Andika — DNA → mRNA (ndani ya kiini)",
      "rna_polymerase_reads_one_dna_strand_3_": "RNA polymerase inasoma strand moja ya DNA 3′→5′ na kujenga RNA 5′→3′. Herufi ni sawa, T tu inakuwa U. mRNA inabeba mapishi hadi ribosome — hatua ya kwanza ya central dogma.",
      "translate_mrna_protein_at_the_ribosome": "Tafsiri — mRNA → protini (kwenye ribosome)",
      "64_codons_20_amino_acids_the_genetic_c": "codon 64 → amino acid 20 (genetic code ina ziada). AUG inaanzisha; UAA/UAG/UGA zinasimamisha. tRNA inasoma codon, inaleta amino acid sahihi, inajenga peptide bond.",
      "mutate_substitution_insertion_deletion": "Badilisha — kubadilisha, kuingiza, kufuta",
      "point_mutation_one_letter_swapped_inse": "Point mutation — herufi moja imebadilishwa. Insertion/deletion — reading frame inahama, protini nzima ya chini inaharibika. Sickle cell anemia ni A→T moja tu — herufi moja, athari ya maisha yote.",
      "crispr_the_precision_edit": "CRISPR — uhariri sahihi",
      "bacterial_immune_system_repurposed_cas": "Mfumo wa kinga wa bakteria umetumiwa upya. Cas9 enzyme + guide RNA = mkasi wa molekuli. Doudna + Charpentier walishinda Nobel 2020. CRISPR therapy ya kwanza (sickle cell) iliidhinishwa na FDA Desemba 2023.",
      "protein_fold_function_malfunction": "Protini — kukunja, kazi, hitilafu",
      "sequence_determines_structure_determin": "Sequence huamua muundo unaoamua kazi. Hemoglobin hubeba O₂, antibody hutambua, enzyme hu-catalyze. AlphaFold (2020) ilitabiri miundo milioni 200 — tatizo la miaka 50 lilitatuliwa ndani ya miezi 18.",
      "forensics_str_profiling_dna_evidence": "Uchunguzi wa kimahakama — STR profiling + ushahidi wa DNA",
      "codis_uses_20_short_tandem_repeat_str_": "CODIS hutumia short tandem repeat (STR) loci 20. Uwezekano wa kufanana ni moja katika quadrillion wakati loci zote zinafanana. Innocence Project — hukumu zaidi ya 245 zisizo sahihi zilifutwa na upimaji wa DNA baada ya kosa.",
      "challenge_graded_problems": "Changamoto — matatizo yaliyopimwa",
      "practice_transcription_translation_mut": "Fanya mazoezi ya transcription, translation, uainishaji wa mutation. AP Bio Big Idea 3.A.1 — DNA (wakati mwingine RNA) ni msingi wa uhamishaji wa taarifa za urithi. NGSS HS-LS3-1.",
      "battle_head_to_head_retrieval": "Vita — kurejesha uso kwa uso",
      "retrieval_practice_gamified_speed_buil": "Mazoezi ya kurejesha — kwa mfumo wa mchezo. Kasi hujenga automaticity — codon table inavyokuwa ya kiotomatiki, working memory yako inakuwa huru kwa fikra za kiwango cha juu, kama kutabiri athari za mutation.",
      "learn_the_central_dogma_history": "Jifunze — central dogma + historia",
      "dna_rna_protein_with_retroviruses_hiv_": "DNA → RNA → protini — ikijumuisha retrovirus (HIV) inayoenda nyuma kwa reverse transcriptase. Crick alibuni neno \"dogma\" mwaka 1957; baadaye alisema linamaanisha dhana, si ukweli usiopingika.",
      "build_a_dna_strand": "Jenga strand ya DNA",
      "pick_a_sequence_the_complementary_stra": "Chagua sequence — strand ya ziada inajazwa na base pairing (A-T, G-C). DNA halisi hujengwa hivi kila wakati.",
      "dna_replication": "DNA replication",
      "helicase_unwinds_the_helix_dna_polymer": "Helicase inafungua helix; DNA polymerase inasoma kila template strand na kuweka ziada yake. Semi-conservative — kila daughter strand ina moja ya zamani + moja mpya.",
      "transcription_dna_mrna": "Transcription — DNA → mRNA",
      "rna_polymerase_reads_the_template_stra": "RNA polymerase inasoma template strand. Sheria ile ile ya complementarity, lakini T → U. Matokeo — nakala moja ya mRNA ya single-strand, tayari kutoka kiini.",
      "translation_mrna_protein": "Translation — mRNA → protini",
      "ribosome_reads_codons_3_bases_at_a_tim": "Ribosome inasoma codon (base 3 kwa wakati). Kila codon → amino acid moja. Genetic code husomwa kama triplet isiyoingiliana, isiyo na koma.",
      "mutations": "Mabadiliko",
      "point_mutations_silent_no_protein_chan": "Point mutation — silent (protini haibadiliki), missense (amino acid moja tofauti), nonsense (kusimama mapema). Frameshift (insertion/deletion) mara nyingi ni ya uharibifu.",
      "crispr_cas9_editing": "CRISPR-Cas9 editing",
      "guide_rna_points_cas9_to_a_20_base_tar": "Guide RNA inaelekeza Cas9 kwenye target ya 20-base. Cas9 inakata strand zote mbili. Njia za urekebishaji za seli hufunga jeni au huongeza template unayotoa.",
      "protein_structure": "Muundo wa protini",
      "primary_sequence_secondary_helix_sheet": "Primary (sequence) → secondary (α-helix, β-sheet) → tertiary (kukunja 3D) → quaternary (multi-subunit). Kubadilika kwa amino acid moja kunaweza kuharibu kukunja.",
      "dna_forensics": "DNA forensics",
